data.Description: ATC has several types to choose from, although trading commission/rates, margin/leverage, deposit requirements etc. appears to be identical per account type. ATC provides a non-dealing desk trading environment, straight through processing (STP) execution, does not have trade restrictions, allows for scalping and is regulated by the NFA. $0.80 round turn for mini contract ($10,000 lot size). $8.00 round turn for a standard contract ($100,000 lot size). Min Deposit is $5,000 USD, however, if you are following a signal system the deposit req. may vary. Institutional price model with Straight Through Processing (STP) order execution through our online trading services. As ATC Brokers does not have a dealing desk environment, they provide variable spreads. The spreads are constantly fluctuating depending on market conditions. Current spread prices can be seen live on their home page: atcbrokers.com/index.php
